data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! NEW! NEW! NEW! Great investment opportunity or home buyer! Located in Academy School D-20! Great access to lots of shopping, restaurants, entertainment, walking trails, I-25 and much more. Newer windows and all new blinds, new interior six panel doors, all new flooring, carpet, paint, lighting, and ceiling fans. Newer wall mount air conditioner. Amazing kitchen with pantry, and all new Whirlpool appliances, side by side refrigerator with water dispenser, new microwave, new range/oven, new dishwasher and disposal. All new cabinets and granite countertops. New oversized stainless kitchen sink with new faucet. Well maintained grass area with built in grill. Extra storage area on upper level. Coin laundry on first floor. HOA includes Covenant enforcement, common utilities, heat, water, lawn maintenance, trash removal and snow removal. (Excludes electricity).
